{"tid":1552811,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"不割不分化 唔好中五毛計","createTime":"2019-09-08T12:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T12:12:46.000Z","uid":104477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4dbfbc7890809144d6830e9113a92ffcf32c4a35","tid":1552811,"uid":104477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:06:34.000Z","msg":"人地都交代左點解由和理非變到依加勇武<br />\n然後出邊一大堆人屌勇武<br />\n再睇返現場根本就冇人怪勇武<br />\n只係連登忽然多人開post屌勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑色五毛警告 正式生效<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五毛分化撚 收皮啦</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd9eb127ae798e8639597141da004a77daa748f5","tid":1552811,"uid":254898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:12:46.000Z","msg":"天琦創業未半，而中道被捕。今天下大亂，香港疲敗，此誠危急存亡之秋也！然文宣之臣，不懈於內；勇武之士，忘身於外者，蓋追天琦之殊遇，欲報之於本土也。誠宜開張聖聽，五大訴求，缺一不可，以光天琦遺德，恢弘時代革命；不宜妄自菲薄，分化割席，以塞光復之路也。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1536001/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1536001/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W79hboU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW79hboU.gif&h=2c39a3c8&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}